{
  "A tank initially contains 200 liters of pure water. A saline solution with 3 g/L concentration flows in at 5 L/min, and the mixed solution flows out at 5 L/min. What is the salt amount after a long time?": "水箱最初含有200升纯水,一种盐碱溶液,5升/分钟的浓度为3克/升,混合溶液流出5升/分钟。",
  "600 grams": "600克",
  "1000 grams": "千克",
  "200 grams": "200克 200克",
  "15 grams": "15克",
  "At equilibrium, the concentration in the tank equals the incoming concentration of 3 g/L. With 200 L in the tank, the salt amount approaches 3 * 200 = 600 grams.": "在平衡时,罐体中的浓度等于流入浓度3克/升。 罐体中含200升,盐量接近3 * 200=600克。",
  "Newton's Law of Cooling gives T(t) = 25 + 75e^(-0.1t). What is the temperature at t = 10?": "牛顿冷却法则给 T(t) = 25 + 75e(-0.1t). t = 10 的温度是多少?",
  "100 degrees, which is a common": "100度,这是常见的",
  "25 degrees, which is a common": "25度,这是常见的",
  "75e^(-1) degrees, which is a common": "75e(-1) 度, 常见",
  "25 + 75e^(-1) (approximately 52.6 degrees)": "25 + 75e(-1)(约52.6度)",
  "T(10) = 25 + 75e^(-0.1*10) = 25 + 75e^(-1) approximately 25 + 27.6 = 52.6 degrees.": "T(10) = 25 + 75e(-0.1*10) = 25 + 75e(-1) 约 25 + 27.6 = 52.6度。",
  "A population model is dP/dt = 0.05P - 100 (births minus emigration). If P(0) = 5000, what is the equilibrium population?": "DP/dt = 0.05P-100(出生减去移民)的人口模式。如果P(0) = 5000,那么平衡人口是什么?",
  "2000": "2000年 2000年",
  "100": "100 100 中 100",
  "5000": "5000( 5000)",
  "0": "0,0",
  "Setting dP/dt = 0: 0.05P - 100 = 0, P = 2000. At this population, births exactly balance emigration.": "设定 dP/dt = 0: 0.05P- 100 = 0, P = 2000 。",
  "A drug is administered intravenously at a constant rate of 50 mg/hr and eliminated at a rate proportional to concentration: dC/dt = 50 - 0.5C. What is the steady-state concentration?": "静脉注射药物以50毫克/小时的恒定速率进行静脉注射,并按浓度比例消除:dC/dt=50 - 0.5C。 稳定状态浓度是多少?",
  "25 mg/L": "25毫克/升",
  "50 mg/L": "50毫克/升",
  "0.5 mg/L": "0.5毫克/升",
  "100 mg/L": "100毫克/升",
  "At steady state, dC/dt = 0: 50 - 0.5C = 0, C = 100 mg/L. Administration rate equals elimination rate at this concentration.": "在稳定状态下,dC/dt = 0: 50 - 0.5C = 0, C = 100 mg/L. 管理率等于这种浓度的消除率。",
  "An object with temperature 200 degrees F is placed in a room at 68 degrees F. After 10 minutes, it is 150 degrees F. Find k in the cooling model.": "温度为200摄氏度的物体放在68摄氏度的房间里。 10分钟后,温度为150摄氏度。 在冷却模型中找到 k。",
  "k = 0.1, particularly in": "k=0.1,特别是:",
  "k = (1/10)ln(132/82) = (1/10)ln(66/41)": "k = 1/10ln(132/82) = 1/10ln(66/41)",
  "k = ln(2)/10, which is a common": "k=在(2)/10中,这是常见的",
  "k = 1/10 regardless of prevailing": "k = 1/10,不管流行程度如何。",
  "T(t) = 68 + 132e^(-kt). At t = 10: 150 = 68 + 132e^(-10k), 82 = 132e^(-10k), e^(-10k) = 82/132 = 41/66. So k = (1/10)ln(66/41).": "T(t) = 68 + 132e(-kt). t = 10: 150 = 68 + 132e(-10k), 82 = 132e(-10k), e__(-10k) = 82/132 = 41/66. 所以k = (1/10)ln(66/41)。",
  "A mortgage has balance B satisfying dB/dt = 0.06B - 2000 (interest minus payments, in dollars/month). If B(0) = 200,000, what is the equilibrium balance?": "抵押贷款余额B满足dB/dt=0.06B-2000(利息减去支付,按美元/月计算)。 如果B(0)=200,000,那么平衡余额是多少?",
  "$200,000": "200 000 000美元",
  "$100,000": "100 000美元",
  "$0": "0美元 0美元",
  "$33,333.33": "33 333.33美元",
  "Setting dB/dt = 0: 0.06B = 2000, B = 2000/0.06 approximately $33,333.33. Since B(0) = 200,000 > 33,333, the balance is increasing (interest exceeds payments). The payment rate is insufficient to pay off the loan.": "设置 dB/dt = 0: 0.06B = 2000, B = 2000/0.06 约33 333.33美元。由于B(0) = 200 000 > 33 333美元,余额在增加(利息超过付款)。支付率不足以偿还贷款。",
  "Carbon-14 dating: a sample has 30% of its original C-14. With half-life 5730 years, how old is it?": "碳-14 日期: 样本拥有其原C-14 的30%。 半衰期5730 岁, 年龄多大 ?",
  "5730 * ln(10/3)/ln(2) years (approximately 9953 years)": "5730 * In(10/3)/ln(2)年(约9953年)",
  "17,190 years, at least according to standard": "17,190年,至少按标准",
  "11,460 years, particularly in the context": "11,460岁,特别是在",
  "5730 years, based on conventional assumptions": "5730年,基于常规假设",
  "N/N_0 = 0.3 = e^(-t*ln2/5730). So t = -5730*ln(0.3)/ln(2) = 5730*ln(10/3)/ln(2) approximately 9953 years.": "N/N_0 = 0.3 = e(-t*ln2/5730). t =-5730*ln(0.3)/ln(2) = 5730*ln(10/3)/ln(2) 大约9953年。",
  "A mixing problem: a 500-gallon tank has 100 gallons of salt water with 2 lb/gal concentration. Pure water flows in at 10 gal/min and the well-mixed solution flows out at 10 gal/min. What is the salt concentration after 20 minutes?": "一个混合问题:500加仑的罐体有100加仑的盐水,浓度为2磅/加仑,纯水流量为10加仑/分钟,混好溶液流量为10加仑/分钟。 20分钟后盐的浓度是多少?",
  "The initial salt is 200 lb; A(t) = 200e^(-t/50). At t = 20: A = 200e^(-0.4). Concentration = 200e^(-0.4)/500 = 0.4e^(-0.4) approximately 0.268 lb/gal": "初始盐为200磅;A(t) = 200e(-t/50);t = 20: A = 200e(-0.4),浓度= 200e(-0.4)/500 = 0.4e(-0.4),约0.268磅/千克。",
  "0 lb/gal, since developments in salt typically cascade through concentration channels to reshape conditions in exactly this manner": "0磅/升/升,因为盐的开发通常通过浓缩渠道逐步升级,以这种方式改变情况",
  "2 lb/gal (unchanged) given that prevailing salt conditions tend to reinforce this particular trajectory": "2升/升/升(不变),因为普遍盐盐条件往往强化这一特定轨迹。",
  "200e^(-20/50) = 200e^(-0.4) lb in 500 gallons, giving concentration 0.4e^(-0.4) lb/gal": "200e(-20/50) = 200e(-0.4) lb, 以500加仑计, 浓度为 0.4e(-0.4) lb/gal",
  "Initial salt: 100 gal * 2 lb/gal = 200 lb. Wait, the tank has 500 gallons total but only 100 of salt water? Actually re-reading: 500-gal tank starts full with concentration 2 lb/gal, so 1000 lb salt. dA/dt = 0 - 10(A/500) = -A/50. A(t) = 1000e^(-t/50). At t=20: A = 1000e^(-0.4). Concentration = 1000e^(-0.4)/500 = 2e^(-0.4) approximately 1.34 lb/gal.": "初始盐:100加仑 * 2磅/gal = 200磅。等等,罐体共有500加仑盐水,但只有100加仑盐水?实际上,再读:500加仑的罐体开始全浓度为2磅/gal, 所以1000磅盐。 dA/dt = 0 - 10 (A/500) = - A/50. A(t) = 1000e(T/50). t= 20: A= 1000e(-0.4). 浓度= 1000e(-0.4)/500 = 2e(-0.4) 约1.34升/gal。",
  "A spring-mass system has velocity v(t) = 3 cos(2t) m/s with initial position x(0) = 0. What is the maximum displacement?": "弹簧质量系统有速度 v(t) = 3 cos(2t) ms/s, 初始位置 x(0) = 0。 最大偏移值是多少?",
  "1.5 meters": "1.5米",
  "3 meters": "3米 3米",
  "6 meters": "6米 6米",
  "0.75 meters": "0.75米",
  "x(t) = integral of 3cos(2t) dt = (3/2)sin(2t) + C. x(0) = 0, so C = 0. x(t) = 1.5 sin(2t). Maximum displacement = 1.5 meters.": "(t) = 3cos(2t) dt = (3/2)sin(2t) + C. x(0) = 0, 所以C = 0. x(t) = 1.5 sin(2t) = 1.5 sin(2t) = (3/2)sin(2t) + C. x(0) = 0, 所以 C = 0. x(t) = 1.5 sin(2t) = 1.5 sin(2t). 最大偏移= 1.5米。",
  "A chemical reaction converts substance A to B at rate dA/dt = -0.2A. If A(0) = 50 grams, how long until 90% has reacted?": "化学反应按dA/dt = -0.2A的速率将A类物质转换为B类。如果A(0) = 50克,在90%之前多久反应?",
  "t = 10 minutes without accounting": "t = 10分钟无会计核算",
  "t = 5 ln(2) minutes when viewed through": "t = 5 = 2 分钟后浏览",
  "t = 5 ln(10) minutes (approximately 11.5 minutes)": "t = 5 In(10)分钟(约11.5分钟)",
  "t = 5 minutes in most scenarios involving": "t = 5分钟 = 5分钟",
  "90% reacted means 10% remains: A = 5. 5 = 50e^(-0.2t), 0.1 = e^(-0.2t), 0.2t = ln(10), t = 5 ln(10) approximately 11.5 minutes.": "90%反应表示剩余10%:A=5 5 = 50e(-0.2t)、0.1 = e(-0.2t)、0.2t = In(10)、t = 5 In(10) 约11.5分钟。",
  "What is a 'mathematical model' in calculus?": "微积分中的数学模型是什么?",
  "A mathematical equation or system of equations that describes a real-world phenomenon and can be analyzed to make predictions": "数学公式或公式系统,描述真实世界现象,并可以分析以作出预测",
  "A statistical summary of data, at least according to standard theory": "数据统计摘要,至少根据标准理论",
  "A graph of any function, which is consistent with how equations mechanisms are understood to operate in theory": "任何函数的图表,该图与方程式机制如何被理解为理论上运作相一致",
  "A physical replica of an object in most scenarios involving equations factors": "在涉及方形因素的大多数假设情景中,物体的物理复制",
  "A mathematical model uses equations (often differential equations) to represent real-world processes. It simplifies reality to capture essential features, allowing prediction, analysis, and optimization.": "数学模型使用方程式(通常是差异方程式)代表现实世界过程。它简化了现实以捕捉基本特征,允许预测、分析和优化。",
  "What does 'rate of change' mean in real-world modeling?": "在现实世界的模型模型中,“变化速度”意味着什么?",
  "The speed of an object within the broader context of change analysis": "在更广泛的变化分析背景下对象的速度",
  "The cost per unit under most circumstances involving change": "多数情况下涉及变动的单位费用",
  "How quickly a quantity changes with respect to time or another variable, expressed as a derivative": "以衍生物表示的时间或另一个变量的数量变化有多快",
  "The total amount of change, based on conventional assumptions about change": "根据关于变动的常规假设作出的变动总额变化总额",
  "Rate of change, expressed as a derivative like dQ/dt, measures how fast a quantity Q is changing at any instant. In modeling, rates of change lead to differential equations that describe system dynamics.": "以像 dQ/dt 这样的衍生物表示的变化率,可以测量数量Q随时变化的速度。在建模中,变化率导致描述系统动态的不同方程式。",
  "What is a 'mixing problem' in differential equations?": "差异方程中的“混合问题”是什么?",
  "A problem that mixes integration and differentiation": "融合和区别兼顾的问题",
  "A problem involving a substance flowing into and out of a container, leading to a differential equation for the amount of substance": "涉及物质流进和流出集装箱的问题,导致物质数量差别方程",
  "A problem about mixing two functions together": "将两个函数混合在一起的问题",
  "An equation with mixed partial derivatives": "配有混合部分衍生物的等式",
  "Mixing problems model the concentration of a substance in a tank as fluid flows in and out. The key equation is dA/dt = (rate in) - (rate out), where the outflow rate depends on the current concentration.": "混合问题将物质在罐体中的浓度作为液体流进和流出的模式。关键方程式是 dA/dt = (速率) - (率) - (率),其中流出率取决于目前的浓度。",
  "What does 'steady state' or 'equilibrium' mean in a real-world model?": "在现实世界模型中,“稳定状态”或“平衡”意味着什么?",
  "A condition where the rate of change is zero, meaning the system is no longer changing over time": "变动率为零的一个条件,意味着系统不再随时间而变化",
  "The initial state of the system": "系统的初始状态",
  "The average value over all time": "整个整个时间的平均值",
  "The maximum value the system can achieve": "系统所能达到的最大值",
  "Steady state occurs when all rates of change equal zero: the system has reached a balance. For example, in a mixing tank, steady state means the inflow and outflow of the substance are equal.": "当所有变化率为零时,就会出现稳定状态:系统已经达到平衡。例如,在混合容器中,稳定状态意味着物质流入和流出是相等的。",
  "What does 'proportionality constant' mean in modeling?": "“比例常数”在建模中意味着什么?",
  "The constant of integration": "融合的常态",
  "A number that equals the proportion of two quantities": "a 等于两个数量比例的数",
  "A constant k that relates two proportional quantities, as in dQ/dt = kQ or F = kx": "与两个比例数量相关的恒定 k, 如 dQ/dt = kQ 或 F = kx",
  "A ratio that changes over time": "随时间变化的比率",
  "A proportionality constant k appears when one quantity is proportional to another. In dQ/dt = kQ, k determines how fast Q grows or decays. It must be determined from data or physical parameters.": "在 dQ/dt = kQ 中, k 确定 Q 生长或衰减的速度。 必须根据数据或物理参数确定 。",
  "What is 'dimensional analysis' in the context of modeling?": "在建模方面,什么是“量分析”?",
  "Measuring the dimensions of an object according to widely held views on this topic": "根据广泛持有的关于这个专题的意见衡量一个物体的维度",
  "Checking that the units on both sides of an equation are consistent, ensuring the model is physically valid": "检查方程两侧的单位是否一致,确保模型实际有效",
  "Counting the number of variables, even when conditions shift significantly": "计数变量数,即使条件发生重大变化",
  "Reducing a 3D problem to 2D under most circumstances involving population": "在多数涉及人口的情况下将3D问题降低到2D",
  "Dimensional analysis verifies that both sides of an equation have the same units. For example, in dP/dt = rP, the left side has units of population/time, and the right side is (1/time)(population) = population/time.": "度量分析证实方程式的两侧都有相同的单位。例如,在 dP/dt = rP 中,左侧有人口/时间单位,右侧为 (1/time(人口) = 人口/时间。",
  "What does 'first-order model' mean?": "\"一等型号\"是什么意思?",
  "The simplest possible model, as conventional first theory would suggest": "最简单的可能模式,如传统第一理论所暗示的",
  "A linear approximation, even when conditions shift significantly": "线性近似值,即使条件发生重大变化",
  "A model that is the first to be tried, especially during periods of significant change": "特别是在发生重大变化的时期首次试用的模式",
  "A model described by a first-order differential equation (involving only the first derivative)": "以第一级差分方程描述的模式(仅涉及第一种衍生物)",
  "A first-order model uses a first-order differential equation (highest derivative is first order). Most models in AP Calculus AB are first-order, including exponential growth/decay, mixing, and logistic models.": "第一阶模型使用第一阶差分方程(最高衍生物为第一阶);AP Calculus AB中的大多数模型为第一阶,包括指数增长/衰减、混合和后勤模型。",
  "What is 'parameter estimation' in modeling?": "建模中“参数估计”是什么?",
  "Estimating how many parameters a model needs, as conventional estimation theory would": "估计模型需要多少参数,作为常规估算理论",
  "Drawing parameters on a graph, especially during periods of significant change": "绘图参数,特别是在发生重大变化的时期",
  "Using measured data to determine the values of unknown constants (parameters) in a mathematical model": "使用测量数据确定数学模型中未知常数(参数)的值",
  "Guessing the solution, even when conditions shift significantly": "猜测解决方案,即使条件发生重大变化",
  "Parameter estimation involves using observed data points to determine values like growth rate k, carrying capacity K, or initial conditions. For example, measuring a population at two times allows solving for k in the exponential model.": "参数估计涉及使用观测到的数据点来确定数值,如增长率 k、承载能力 K 或初始条件。例如,两次测量人口,可以解决指数模型中的 k。",
  "What does 'model validation' mean?": "\"模型验证\"是什么意思?",
  "Proving the model is mathematically correct": "证明模型在数学上是正确的",
  "Checking that the equation has a solution": "检查方程式是否有解决方案",
  "Comparing the model's predictions with actual data to determine if the model accurately represents reality": "将模型的预测与实际数据进行比较,以确定模型是否准确反映现实",
  "Certifying the model for publication": "核证公布模式的核证",
  "Model validation tests whether the mathematical model's predictions match observed data. If predictions deviate significantly from reality, the model assumptions may need to be revised.": "模型验证测试数学模型的预测是否与观察到的数据相符,如果预测明显偏离现实,则可能需要修订模型假设。",
  "What is a 'compartment model'?": "什么是“区划模型”?",
  "A model stored in separate compartments of a computer": "存放在计算机分隔区中的模型",
  "A model that separates variables": "区分变量的模型",
  "A model with multiple solutions": "具有多重解决方案的模型",
  "A model that divides a system into distinct compartments (like a tank), tracking the flow of material between them": "一种模式,将一个系统分成不同的隔开区(如罐体),跟踪它们之间的材料流动",
  "A compartment model tracks the amount of a substance in one or more compartments (tanks, organs, populations) as it flows between them. Mixing problems and pharmacokinetic models are examples of compartment models.": "一个隔板模型在一个或多个隔板(坦克、器官、人口)中跟踪物质在它们之间流动的数量,混合问题和药动能模型是隔板模型的例子。",
  "A water treatment plant has a 10,000-gallon tank. Contaminated water (0.05 lb/gal of pollutant) flows in at 100 gal/min and the well-mixed solution exits at 100 gal/min. If the tank initially has pure water, what is the pollutant amount after 30 minutes?": "水处理厂有一个10 000加仑的罐体,被污染的水(0.05升/升/升)以100加仑/分钟的速度流出,混合的溶液以100加仑/分钟的速度流出,如果罐体最初有净水,30分钟后污染物的含量是多少?",
  "500 pounds when considering all relevant water": "考虑所有相关水时500磅",
  "50 pounds regardless of prevailing conditions": "不论目前条件如何,50磅",
  "500(1 - e^(-0.3)) pounds (approximately 129.7 pounds)": "500(1 - e(-0.3)磅(约129.7磅)",
  "150 pounds, as conventional water theory would": "150磅 传统水理论",
  "dA/dt = 0.05(100) - (A/10000)(100) = 5 - A/100. Solution: A(t) = 500(1 - e^(-t/100)). At t = 30: A = 500(1 - e^(-0.3)) approximately 500(0.259) = 129.7 pounds.": "dA/dt = 0.05(100) - (A/1000)(100) = 5 - A/100. 解决方案: A(t) = 500(1 - e__(t/100). t = 30: A = 500(1 - e__(0.3)) 约500(0.259) =129.7磅。",
  "A scientist heats a substance from room temperature (20 degrees C) to a target of 200 degrees C in an oven at 250 degrees C. The heating follows dT/dt = 0.05(250 - T). How long to reach 200 degrees C?": "科学家将一种物质从室内温度(20摄氏度)加热到在250摄氏度的烤箱中达到200摄氏度的目标。 供暖过程遵循dT/dt = 0.05(250-T)。 要达到200摄氏度多久?",
  "40 minutes": "40分钟40分钟",
  "20 ln(2) minutes": "20 英寸(2)分",
  "20 minutes": "20分钟20分钟",
  "20 ln(230/50) = 20 ln(23/5) minutes": "20 in(230/50) = 20 in(23/5) 分钟",
  "T(t) = 250 - 230e^(-0.05t). Setting T = 200: 200 = 250 - 230e^(-0.05t), 230e^(-0.05t) = 50, e^(-0.05t) = 50/230 = 5/23, t = -20 ln(5/23) = 20 ln(23/5).": "T(t) = 250 - 230e(- 0.05t). 设置 T = 200: 200 = 250 - 230e(- 0.05t), 230e(- 0.05t) = 50, e(- 0.05t) = 50/230 = 5/23, t = - 20 In( 5/23) = 20 In( 23/5) 。",
  "A loan of $50,000 accrues interest at 6% continuously and is paid back at $500/month. The balance satisfies dB/dt = 0.06B - 500. Will the loan be paid off?": "50 000美元的贷款连续累积利息6%,每月500美元偿还,余额满足dB/dt = 0.06B-500。贷款将偿还吗?",
  "Yes, in about 20 years when the interaction between loan and balance factors is taken into full account": "是的,大约在20年的时间里,贷款和平衡因素之间的相互作用得到充分考虑",
  "Yes, in about 10 years, since standard models of loan behavior predict this outcome under normal conditions": "是的,大约十年了,因为贷款行为标准模式在正常条件下预测了这一结果",
  "The balance stays constant at $50,000, especially during periods of significant change": "余额维持在50 000美元不变,特别是在发生重大变化期间",
  "No; the equilibrium is B = 500/0.06 approximately $8333, and since B(0) = 50000 > 8333, the balance grows without bound": "否;平衡为B=500/0.06,约8 333美元,自B(0)=50000 >8333以来,平衡无约束地增长",
  "The equilibrium is at B = 500/0.06 approximately $8333. Since B(0) = 50000 > 8333 and the model gives dB/dt = 0.06(50000) - 500 = 2500 > 0, the balance is increasing. The monthly payment is insufficient to cover the interest, so the loan grows indefinitely.": "由于B(0) = 50000 > 8333, 模型给出dB/dt = 0.06 (500-500) = 2500 > 0, 余额正在增加。 每月支付不足以支付利息, 因此贷款将无限期增长 。",
  "A forensic scientist uses Newton's Law of Cooling to estimate time of death. A body is found at 85 degrees F in a 70 degree F room. One hour later, it is 80 degrees F. Normal body temperature is 98.6 degrees F. Approximately how long ago did death occur?": "法医科学家使用牛顿冷却法估计死亡时间。在70度F房中发现尸体在85度F,一小时后为80度F。正常身体温度为98.6度F。大约多久前死亡?",
  "Approximately 10 hours before discovery": "大约在发现前10小时",
  "Approximately 3.5 hours before discovery": "大约在发现前3.5小时",
  "Approximately 5 hours before discovery": "大约在发现前5小时",
  "Approximately 1 hour before discovery": "大约在发现前1小时",
  "T(t) = 70 + Ce^(-kt) where t is measured from death. At discovery: 85 = 70 + Ce^(-kt_d), so Ce^(-kt_d) = 15. One hour later: 80 = 70 + Ce^(-k(t_d+1)), so Ce^(-k(t_d+1)) = 10. Dividing: e^(-k) = 10/15 = 2/3, k = ln(3/2). At death (t=0): 98.6 = 70 + C, C = 28.6. From Ce^(-kt_d) = 15: 28.6e^(-kt_d) = 15, e^(-kt_d) = 15/28.6, kt_d = ln(28.6/15). t_d = ln(28.6/15)/ln(3/2) approximately 0.645/0.405 approximately 1.59 hours before discovery. With the extra hour: about 2.6 hours total. Given approximations, about 3.5 hours is a reasonable estimate accounting for measurement uncertainty.": "T( t) = 70 + Ce (- kt) = 70 + Ce (- kt_ d) 。 发现时: 85 = 70 + Ce (- kt_ d) = 15. 1 小时后: 80 = 70 + Ce (- k( t_ d+ 1) ) , 所以 Ce (- k( t_ d+ 1) = 10. Dividid: e (- k) = 10/ 15 = 2/3, k = In( 3/ 3) 。 发现时: 98.6 = 70 + C, C = 28.6 (- kt_ d) = 15. 15 e (- kt_ d) , 所以 Ce ( ) = e (28.6/15), kt_ d = IN( 28.6/15) t_ d ) = 10, 0. 45/ 0 005 约 1. 59 小时前发现。 小时后, 估计为 2.6小时的不确定性。",
  "A forest fire burns area at a rate proportional to the perimeter of the burned circle: dA/dt = k*sqrt(A). If A(0) = 100 acres and A(2) = 400 acres, find k.": "与烧毁的圆圈周边成比例的森林火灾燃烧面积:dA/dt = k*sqrt(A)。如果A(0) = 100英亩,A(2) = 400英亩,则见k。",
  "k = 150 according to widely held views on this": "k = 150, 根据对此广泛持有的意见。",
  "k = 5, particularly in the context of acres": "k=5,特别是英亩面积",
  "k = 20 when viewed through a simplified analytical": "k = 20,通过简化分析查看。",
  "k = 10 (using the solution 2*sqrt(A) = kt + 2*sqrt(100))": "k=10(使用溶液2*sqrt(A)=kt+2*sqrt(100))",
  "Separate: A^(-1/2) dA = k dt. Integrate: 2A^(1/2) = kt + C. At t = 0: 2(10) = C, C = 20. At t = 2: 2(20) = 2k + 20, 40 = 2k + 20, k = 10.": "分号:A(-1/2)dA = kdt. 整合: 2A(1/2) = kt + C。在 t = 0: 2(10) = C, C = 20. t = 2 2: 2(20) = 2k + 20, 40 = 2k + 20, k = 10。",
  "A company's revenue satisfies dR/dt = 0.1R(1 - R/1000000) (logistic growth in dollars, K = $1M). With R(0) = $50,000, when does R reach $500,000?": "一家公司的收入达到 dR/dt = 0.1R(1 - R/1000,000美元)(以美元计的物流增长,K = 100万美元),R(0) = 50,000美元,R何时达到500,000美元?",
  "t = 50 time units": "t = 50 小时单位",
  "t = 10 ln(10) time units": "t = 10 In(10) 时间单位",
  "t = 10 time units": "t = 10个时单位",
  "t = 10 ln(19) time units (approximately 29.4 time units)": "t = 10 In( 19) 时间单位( 约29.4 时间单位)",
  "R(t) = 1000000/(1 + 19e^(-0.1t)). Setting R = 500000: 2 = 1 + 19e^(-0.1t), 19e^(-0.1t) = 1, e^(-0.1t) = 1/19, t = 10 ln(19) approximately 29.4.": "R(t) = 10000/(1 + 19e(-0.1t)) 设置 R = 500000: 2 = 1 + 19e(-0.1t), 19e(-0.1t) = 1, e(-0.1t) = 1/19, t = 10 In(19) 约29.4。",
  "A polluted lake has 500 tons of pollutant. Clean water flows in and polluted water flows out, following dP/dt = -P/10. Environmental regulations require P < 50 tons. How long until compliance?": "污染湖有500吨污染物,在DP/dt = -P/10之后,清洁水流和污染水流流出,环境条例要求P < 50吨。",
  "50 years without accounting": "50年(无会计核算)",
  "100 years, as conventional flows": "100年,作为传统流动",
  "10 years, especially during periods": "10岁,特别是10至10岁,特别是在",
  "10 ln(10) years (approximately 23 years)": "10年(10年)(约23年)",
  "P(t) = 500e^(-t/10). Set P = 50: 50 = 500e^(-t/10), e^(-t/10) = 0.1, t/10 = ln(10), t = 10 ln(10) approximately 23 years.": "P(t) = 500e(- t/10). 设定P = 50: 50 = 500e(- t/10), e(- t/10) = 0.1, t/10 = In(10), t = 10 In(10) 约23年。",
  "An airplane's fuel consumption rate is dF/dt = -(200 + 0.5v) gallons per hour at velocity v mph. If v = 500 mph is constant and the plane starts with 10,000 gallons, how long can it fly?": "飞机的燃料消耗速率是每小时DF/dt=-(200+0.5v)加仑,速度为每小时0.5mph。如果 v=500mph是恒定的,飞机开始时用1万加仑,它能飞多久?",
  "10000/200 = 50 hours": "10000/200=50小时",
  "50 hours": "50小时50时",
  "20 hours": "20时20分",
  "10000/450 approximately 22.2 hours": "大约22.2时左右",
  "At v = 500: dF/dt = -(200 + 250) = -450 gal/hr. F(t) = 10000 - 450t. Set F = 0: t = 10000/450 approximately 22.2 hours.": "V = 500: dF/dt = - (200+250) = - 450 gal/hr. F(t) = 10000 - 450t. Set F = 0: t = 10000/450 大约22.2小时。",
  "A patient takes medication that enters the bloodstream at 30 mg/hr and is eliminated at rate 0.1C mg/hr, where C is the current concentration. The model is dC/dt = 30 - 0.1C. If C(0) = 0, what is C(10)?": "患者服用的药物以30毫克/小时进入血液流,以0.1C毫克/小时(C是目前的浓度)的速率消除。该模型为dC/dt=30 - 0.1C。如果C(0)=0,那么C(10)是什么?",
  "100 mg/L, at least according to standard": "100毫克/升,至少按标准",
  "30 mg/L, even when conditions shift": "30毫克/升,即使条件改变",
  "300 mg/L, even when conditions shift": "300毫克/升,即使条件改变",
  "300(1 - e^(-1)) mg/L (approximately 189.5 mg/L)": "300(1 - e(-1)) mg/L(约189.5 mg/L)",
  "C(t) = 300(1 - e^(-0.1t)). At t = 10: C = 300(1 - e^(-1)) approximately 300(0.632) = 189.5 mg/L.": "C(t) = 300(1 - e__(-0.1t). t = 10: C = 300(1 - e__(-1).) 约 300(0.632) = 189.5毫克/升.",
  "A city's traffic flow model gives the number of cars on a highway as N(t), with dN/dt = 500 - 0.05N^2. At what value of N does traffic reach equilibrium?": "城市交通流量模式给出了N(t)的高速公路上的汽车数量,DN/dt=500 - 0.05N2. 交通量达到平衡的N值是多少?",
  "N = 500 cars, especially during periods": "N=500辆汽车,特别是在期间",
  "N = 100 cars (since sqrt(500/0.05) = sqrt(10000) = 100)": "N=100辆汽车(自Sqrt(500/0.05) = sqrt(1000) = 100)",
  "N = 50 cars according to widely held views": "N=50辆汽车,根据广泛持有的意见",
  "N = 10000 cars, at least according to standard": "N=10 000辆汽车,至少按照标准",
  "Equilibrium: dN/dt = 0, so 500 = 0.05N^2, N^2 = 10000, N = 100 cars (taking the positive root).": "平衡:dN/dt = 0, 所以500 = 0.05N2, N2 = 10000, N = 100 辆汽车( 正根)。"
